# International Communist League: We share the pain of the people of all nations that have lost their lives due to the earthquake in Turquia, Rojava and Norte Syria!

Author: SERVIR AL PUEBLO

Publish Time: 2023-03-02T06:34:57+00:00

Modified Time: 2023-03-02T06:34:57+00:00

