. Today, there is no such Communist Party, but there are communists, in accordance, revolutionary and anti-imperialists that must be will There is no communist party. Without the Communist Party, democracy for the people, or National Liberation, or Revolution cannot have a revolution. The most advanced revolutionary forces must be ideologically, politically, morally and materially, so that they can move forward, under the main difficulties they face, in the struggle for the reconstitution of communist participation; This is the key task.As President Mao has taught, the communists do not fear the Guerramundial, we do not fear nuclear war, we are against them and we will do everything to prevent it by developing the revolution, to combat the warfare with popular war. By condemning the imperialist aggression and algerrerismo of the imperialists we can never forget this: the imperialist aggression must be defeated with the popular war.

