++ Press Conference Thursday 2 March at 3:00 pm entry of the Polytechnic into viaorbona ++

Six militants of our organization, all students of the Dibari University, were searched and reported on Saturday 25 Febbioper had exhibited a banner in front of the Polytechnic - then seized - didizer against the agreements between the university and the war industries, one ' Action commercial

In connection with the national event called by the workers to be workers in Genoa who saw on the same day to go to the square over the opposition to the war and where, as students and university students, we mobilized alongside the struggle to block the weapons in the ports.

We immediately want to make it clear that we will not back these intimidation in the least, we are convinced of the reasons for our protest Edel that within our universities must be guaranteed space for political and democratic diagibilities.

Our organization has long been engaged in bringing the illness of the numerous relations between the war and academic world to the open. Nonsolo the Polytechnic but also the Uniba are, in fact, at the center of a massive operation that sees the war industries and the defense ministry in the front row in the perspective of a military strengthening of the Mediterranean dial.

The ongoing war in Ukraine, which involves Italy within the NATO Alleanzaatlantica, is leading to a stiffening of the control on the "internal front" and to an restlessness of political control over what Chesi moves in the country and therefore also in universities But they will not be these to stop our struggles. With even greater conviction, let's continue mobilization, let's make an appointment on Thursday 2 March at 15:00 at the entrance to the entrance orbona of the Polytechnic of Bari for a press conference.

