## Meloni in Nuova Delhi: highly strategic partnership relationships, announced the start of joint exercises

The commercial exchange between Italy and India is almost 15 billion euros, a datumped in just two years

March 2, 2023

[__](https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.agenzianova.com%2Fnews%2Fmeloni-a-nuova-delhi-relazioni-italia-india-elevate-a-partenariato-strategico-annunciato-lavvio-di-esercitazioni-congiunte%2F"Facebook")[__](https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Meloni+a+Nuova+Delhi%3A+relazioni+elevate+a+partenariato+strategico%2C+annunciato+l%E2%80%99avvio+di+esercitazioni+congiunte&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.agenzianova.com%2Fnews%2Fmeloni-a-nuova-delhi-relazioni-italia-india-elevate-a-partenariato-strategico-annunciato-lavvio-di-esercitazioni-congiunte%2F&via=agenzia_nova"Twitter")[__](https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=Meloni+a+Nuova+Delhi%3A+relazioni+elevate+a+partenariato+strategico%2C+annunciato+l%E2%80%99avvio+di+esercitazioni+congiunte%0A%0A https://www.agenzianova.com/news/meloni-a-nuova-delhi-relazioni-italia-india-elevate-a-partenariato-strategico-annunciato-lavvio-di-esercitazioni-congiunte/ "WhatsApp")[__](Mailto:? Subject = Meloni to Nuova Delhi: Relating to strategic partnership, announced the start of exercisexcontiunta & body = https: //www.agenzianova.com/news/meloni-a-delhi- Italy-inia- elevate- a-parthenariat-Strategico-Annunciata-start-of-Esercitazioni-Concunte/ "email")

[![](Images/proletari comunisti/2023-03-02T12-00-00-01-00/FqMiDhMaEAAEF8C-e1677747908232-696x484.jpg)](https://www.agenzianova.com/news/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/FqMiDhMaEAAEF8C-e1677747908232.jpg)



The commercial interchange between Italy and India is almost 15 billion euros, a datum doubled in just two years, Meloni clarified. "We can do it from: the recovery of direct flights, for example, can facilitate strengthening relationships," added Meloni, who then spoke of the multesimilitudes between the two countries. "Millennial cultures, states who have fought independence and freedom," said the Italian premier. For the Meloni ** Defense and energy security, Meloni are between the sectors where Italy and India want to strengthen bilateral relationships **. "There is also an atema of the digital transition, with very important projects that connect Lenostre two nations," he added.

![](Images/proletari comunisti/2023-03-02T12-00-00-01-00/FqMlT3IaEAEikMZ-1024x835.jpg)President Meloni also spoke of migrations explaining that the agreement is India and Italy "has a particular importance". "His conclusion-long has added to further conforcies the relationships between peoples," explained Premier, adding that the parties also have the intention of "strengthening cooperation at the higher education level".

The Prime Minister was received by the Indian premier at the ** Rashtrapati Bhawan **, the presidential palace. The arrival of the premier was greeted by the picket of honor of the armed forces. It is the bilateral primoviaggio in Asia since the beginning of the mandate, in the 75th anniversary of relations between India and Italy.India and Italy are "side by side in the fight against terrorism and allesparatism" he continued. "We had an interview on how to strengthen cooperation," said the premier. The head of the Government of NewDelhi stressed that the relationships between the two countries, both of the heirs of the Dyriatic civilizations, "have always been" and that with Meloni he spoke of coming to these relations "a new form adequate for the needs of the timing -tence".

India and Italy celebrate the 75th anniversary of their relationships by becoming strategic partners and strengthening the economic bonds, HasottoLineate still the President Modi. The campaign for the promotion of the Indian industry("Make in India")and the mission for an Indiautosufficica("Self -sufficient India")They are opening "immense opportunities for the flood in India", underlined the head of the new Delhi government, adding that it was particularly placed in the emphasis on the expansion of eco -work in areas such as renewable energy, green hydrogen, IT lawsters, i Semiconductors, telecommunications and space. Inoltre, an initiative dedicated to start-ups is now announced.

Meloni previously visited the memorial dedicated to the father of the Nazioneindiana, ** Mahatma Gandhi **, at Raj Ghat. "'There are few examples of man in the world who, alone, has accomplished the resurrection of his country with the laphrza of thought and the extreme dedication lasting his whole life'. So Ilgrande Mahatma Gandhi spoke of Giuseppe Mazzini, one of the fathers of the Italianrisorgimento, A source of inspiration also for the Indian one. Two -plays that with their actions and their works indicated the Ainostri peoples' path, "added the premier.



