# India: Modi in conflict with the BBC

Author: Tjen Folket Media

Description: The British state channel has revealed through a new documentary, including that India's Prime Minister Narendra Modi has actively contributed to the persecution of the country's Muslims.

Publish Time: 2023-03-02T14:26:34+00:00

Modified Time: 2023-03-02T14:26:37+00:00

Images: ['[Modi-India-1160x716.jpg](https://tjen-folket.no/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Modi-India-1160x716.jpg)']

Tags: None

Category: 'Asia'

<!--METADATA-->

![](Images/Tjen-Folket/2023-03-02T14-26-34-00-00/Modi-India-1160x716.jpg)* * *

By a commentator for the Earn Folket Media.

* * *

** The British state channel has through a new documentary, including revealed India's Prime Minister Narendra Modi has actively contributed to the persecution of the abroad Muslims. **

Our Indian comrades in India's Communist Party(Maoistene)Characterizes the government as fascist, and Indian "democracy" as a interest rush democracy. The persecution of religious and ethnic minorities is a recognition signs for this regime, and Modi represents the party BJP and Denhindu fascist activist organization RSS, which is in reality behind the party.

