# 02/03: Andes Motion against the slaughter in Nova Mutum in Rondônia during the repossession operation

Author:  Postado por

 Time: 2023-03-02T14:55:00-03:00

Images: ['[AVvXsEgl3d1MijwgIrjWMzSzFV-nhKC2H6GkKqTJZ3u863P24jBaSjR1ed5MzRprXJUor8nnyE0urTnDZKBA899LJ56FhF9BGqRIpASchDWy-0BXHedDg-xrmBNvO3J4SxNGmKu5dAmt4l18789aIb32H0guTwwcc7riu5_MI71hZH-TYi1mjpn1q9bnxoP6zg](https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgl3d1MijwgIrjWMzSzFV-nhKC2H6GkKqTJZ3u863P24jBaSjR1ed5MzRprXJUor8nnyE0urTnDZKBA899LJ56FhF9BGqRIpASchDWy-0BXHedDg-xrmBNvO3J4SxNGmKu5dAmt4l18789aIb32H0guTwwcc7riu5_MI71hZH-TYi1mjpn1q9bnxoP6zg)']

<!--METADATA-->

We reproduce here the Motion of Repudiation of the National Union of Teachers of Higher Education - Andes -SN.

________________________________________________________________



[![](Images/CEBRASPO/2023-03-02T14-55-00-03-00/AVvXsEgl3d1MijwgIrjWMzSzFV-nhKC2H6GkKqTJZ3u863P24jBaSjR1ed5MzRprXJUor8nnyE0urTnDZKBA899LJ56FhF9BGqRIpASchDWy-0BXHedDg-xrmBNvO3J4SxNGmKu5dAmt4l18789aIb32H0guTwwcc7riu5_MI71hZH-TYi1mjpn1q9bnxoP6zg)](https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/a/AVvXsEgl3d1MijwgIrjWMzSzFV-nhKC2H6GkKqTJZ3u863P24jBaSjR1ed5MzRprXJUor8nnyE0urTnDZKBA899LJ56FhF9BGqRIpASchDWy-0BXHedDg-xrmBNvO3J4SxNGmKu5dAmt4l18789aIb32H0guTwwcc7riu5_MI71hZH-TYi1mjpn1q9bnxoP6zg)** Motion of repudiation **

** ** O(A)S Delegate(a)those present to the 41st Congress of the National Andes-Syndicate, held in Rio Branco(AC), from February 6 to 10 ,2023, they express repudiation of the slaughter in Nova Mutum in Rondônia, during an operation of repossession at the headquarters of Norbrasil Farm. And in the face of the complaints, we endorse the collection of the lawyers of the people:

**1)Federal Intervention for the Calculation and Accountability of the Police Developed in the Execution of Peasants; **

**two)The resumption of the property for the union and destination for the settlement of the Family of the camp Tiago Campin dos Santos; **

** 3)Identification and criminal liability of gunmen who were in judgment threatening the peasants; **

** 4)Liability of the state of Rondônia for the crimes committed by the year agents; It is**

** 5)** ** Return of the belongings of the families who stayed in the shed of Fazendas. **

** For the end of crimes against the poor peasants of Rondônia!Earth for those who work!**

On January 28, Raniel Barbosa Laurindo(known as "mandruvá")de24 years and Rodrigo Hawerroth(known as "stretched"), 34 years old, after -torture after torture by the PM of Rondônia, as reported by the Poor Dospempion League - LCP, the Brazilian Center for Solidarity to Peoples and the Brazilian Lawyers Association - Abrapo.[Verrelating](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XGrO5QS8FWQilyKSLykrHW2SRLharrNJ/view)Violence in the state of Rondônia, more specifically in the region between Odistrito de Nova Mutum-Paraná and Nova Dimension, in the municipality of Nova Mamoré, has intensified in the last two years. Only at Camp Tiago Campindos Santos 11 deaths have been registered since 2021. Commission complaints from the land and the League of the poor peasants of Rondônia point out quiemilicia and public authorities of the state are responsible for the extremeness experienced by the peasants in Rondônia.



Since 2020, the peasants of this region have been terrified by the police soba orders of Governor Colonel Marcos Rocha, with successive slaughter, torture and arrests of peasants. Rural militias, pistolage and land grabbing have been encouraged and supported by the state in an alliance with the lathifaces. The supposed owner of those lands is the company Lememprondimentos, by the landowner Antônio Martins, "Rooster Velho", as he is known in the region, is quoted in the "White Book of Land Shot" as a larger land grabbers in the country, is being investigated by the Civil Police Epaderal , together with the Public Prosecution Service, for the financing of the region for land grabbing and expulsion of peasants.

News Source: [https://cebraspo.blogspot.com/2023/03/0203-mocao-de-repudio-do-andes-contra.html](https://cebraspo.blogspot.com/2023/03/0203-mocao-de-repudio-do-andes-contra.html)

