# Protests of servers across the country require rights - the new democracy

Author: Giovanna Maria

Description: Municipal Public Servants have performed strikes requiring salary adjustments, better working conditions and rejecting anti-sore reforms.

Publish Time: 2023-03-02T16:31:43-03:00

Modified Time: 2023-03-02T16:36:59-03:00

Updated Time: 2023-03-02T16:36:59-03:00

Images: ['[sintrapp-1.webp](https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/sintrapp-1.webp)', '[svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjEgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBzdHlsZT0iZmlsbDojY2ZkNGRiO2ZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eTogMC4xOyIvPjwvc3ZnPg==](https://anovademocracia.com.brdata:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjEgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBzdHlsZT0iZmlsbDojY2ZkNGRiO2ZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eTogMC4xOyIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)']

Section: Nacional

Tags: ['greve', 'Luta Classista', 'Servidores públicos']

Type: article

<!--METADATA-->

![](ConvertedIMGs/A Nova Democracia/2023-03-02T16-31-43-03-00/sintrapp-1.png)Municipal servants started strike in Presidente Prudente(SP). Foto: Itamar Batista/AI/Sintrapp

Servidores públicos municipais têm realizado greves exigindo  reajustessalariais, melhores condições de trabalho e rechaçando reformas anti-povo. Asmobilizações ocorreram nos estados de Paraíba (PB), São Paulo(SP)and Paraná(PR)at the end of February and early March.

In the city of ** Presidente Prudente(** SP), municipal servants that we earn less salaries in the city of the city executive went on strike nodia March 1. The strike participates the library assistants, telephone auxiliaries, cooks, bricklayer servants, general services and watches. They claim better working conditions and salaries for acateutor.

They are workers of the so -called “reference 1”, type of “progression” or “level” salary in which workers are placed. The stoppage is for time.

According to Sintrapp president Luciana Telles, the current Mayor Prudente Mayor Ed Thomas(partyless), he had promised during an electoral camp that he would pay special attention to the servers' claims that they receive less, but nothing has been done so far. According to the president, they receive less than one minimum wage. City proposals account for an increase of 10% of the salary, which would give about R $ 100 for workers.

![](Images/A Nova Democracia/2023-03-02T16-31-43-03-00/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjEgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBzdHlsZT0iZmlsbDojY2ZkNGRiO2ZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eTogMC4xOyIvPjwvc3ZnPg==)Foz do Iguaçu Municipal Servants fight against pension reform. Photo: Portalda Cidade

In ** Foz do Iguaçu **, in Paraná, more than 6,000 servers from various sectors participated from a joint general meeting on 25/02 that rejected the renovated municipal social security. The workers demarcated that if theirxigences are not attended to, they will take a strike.

In addition, more than two thousand education servers in the city are already comminlishing strike and requires the 4.89% pendants referring to the readjustment of the padonational of the 2022 teaching.In the municipality of ** Bayeux **(PB), on March 1, the general strike was began indefinitely. Workers reject the bundled wages of different categories, the non -payment of the January 2022 retroactive for vigilantes, the non -implementation of the national floor and the non -payment of a night and unhealthy surveys.

In ** bauru **(SP), on 03/05, municipal servants will meet for a general meeting, who will decide on the workers' strike. ASCATEGORIES require a 24.37%readjustment, which, even with surpluses in the last two years, the city refuses to pay.

