The Meloni Warning Hair government and its "Atlanticism" found the Stradaspianata by the Draghi government in particular by the Democratic Party with the former Minister Guerrini. Today the relations of Italy-LATE/USA mean increased military spending, Armedi Ucraine(The estimate is 800 million, also voted by the new secretary Pd, Schlein), Italian expansionism from the Mediterranean to Indo-Pacific.

[![](Images/proletari comunisti/2023-03-02T17-55-00-01-00/Crosetto-generale%20Milley.jpg)](https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjoeytcX-0ggS6ZgCxe60NlSYjE2LFtPm2YKgU4JXQWkdsPoAczm1qYlLgFCQ_ycEPgQg4TGlfM3y066u0ijP_smJQ651mivDPWwCsZ1ZlQdivB9pduMlgSzQGEsXgCutDxUhEXud8vdrPJKxslD7iYNilUWftkvVCQz-sNa0yG2pJTTtgFEwq-L7yh8Q/s628/Crosetto-generale%20Milley.jpg)** _ "Relations between Italy and the US cover high strategic relevance. The current general security framework also requires more than corn bilateral relationships today". So Minister Crosetto meeting the Generalmilley, chief of staff of the American armed forces ._ **

[![](Images/proletari comunisti/2023-03-02T17-55-00-01-00/wired-spese%20militari.jpg)](https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg7kZPmexa1x1Ca2eyDijcknz35E9d8bXQ0QhO47HVO1ws7pAPrJ8jLFNPj_kCbQLt4Sc9d6gOu3Ey_O_KYm0S_pWRoUxM0rjyxdhVm_f893Go90B-vrEgkidNICAIIFavGARZ6kdBHuYRmtDQ-zOPpTge38DsX940Otmryp1K_k9LPJ1h0N-C-U6yq8w/s978/wired-spese%20militari.jpg)from Wired

In the autumn of 2022, the draft project of the Ministry of Defense arrives on the Chamber and Senate benches. It concerns drones capable of saying the stratosphere. In the report there are some details on the futuredrons(For example, it will serve for intelligence purposes, boundary control had had weather data)and much less on who will take care of it(the industrialional, ok, but who?)and where. And then there are the estimates of the money necessary. Sore man. At least 20 million, while already putting black on white that in the 13 years of duration of the program(2022-2034)It will cost at least double: 55 million euros.

